*Protiv* njih nismo imali šansi. (We didn't have a chance against them.)

Moje mišljenje je *protiv* njihovog. (My opinion is against theirs.)

*Protiv* se nisam mogao boriti. (I couldn't fight against it.)

Ne mogu da se izborim *protiv* njihovih laži. (I can't fight against their lies.)

Moj sin je išao *protiv* mojih želja. (My son went against my wishes.)